snippet.textDisplay:
Overwhelmed to receive so much love to the song. Thankful to Coke Studio team to allow us  to retain the classical Kashmiri Wanwun in the composition.  Translation was also done while keeping cultural sensibilities in both languages in consideration. All in all, the magic that we all conceived for the song  is getting transported into reality. Lassiv, Pholiv, Aabad rooziv.

-Rumuz.
